snippet.title: Amber Rose Gives Her Definition of a 'Sl*t', Reacts to Men Being 'Sl*t Makers' (Part 2)
snippet.description:
Watch Part 3: https://goo.gl/CYS9h1
Part 1: https://goo.gl/Ag6XKD
----------------------------------------
In her interview with The Fallen State TV, Amber Rose spoke with Jesse Lee Peterson about Bill Cosby's rape case, along with her definition of what is a slut. She explained to Peterson that Bill Cosby in the 90s was on par with Barack Obama today, adding that no one would've believed them if his accusers spoke out back then.

During the conversation, Rose reacted to Peterson calling men who sleep with a lot of women "slut makers," and told him that she would refer to herself as a slut. To hear more, hit the above clip.

Video credit: The Fallen State TV

Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/thefallenstatetv

Website: http://thefallenstate.tv/fallenstate/
